<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Elliot Mitchell | Creative Tech Portfolio</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    :root { --bg:#0a0a0f; --fg:#f8f9ff; --muted:#b8bdd7; }
    body { margin:0; font-family:'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background:radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%,#1f2a60,#0a0a0f 36%), radial-gradient(circle at 85% 0%,#49266f,#0a0a0f 42%); color:var(--fg); }
    .shell { width:min(1180px,94%); margin:0 auto; padding:34px 0 46px; }
    .hero { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.2fr .8fr; gap:18px; align-items:stretch; }
    @media(max-width:900px){ .hero { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
    .glass { backdrop-filter: blur(8px); background:rgba(10,12,24,.6); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); border-radius:18px; padding:26px; }
    .badge { display:inline-block; background:linear-gradient(120deg,#8df8d8,#7da8ff,#d487ff); color:#07101f; padding:7px 11px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:800; font-size:.8rem; }
    h1 { margin:12px 0; font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5.5vw,4rem); line-height:1.05; }
    .subtitle { color:var(--muted); max-width:680px; font-size:1.05rem; }
    .cta a { color:#fff; text-decoration:none; margin-right:14px; font-weight:700; }
    .mosaic { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr); gap:12px; margin-top:14px; }
    .tile { border-radius:14px; padding:16px; min-height:150px; background:rgba(17,22,40,.74); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
    .tile h2 { margin:0 0 9px; font-size:1rem; }
    .tile p, .tile li { color:var(--muted); font-size:.95rem; }
    .span-3{grid-column:span 3;} .span-2{grid-column:span 2;} .span-1{grid-column:span 1;} .span-4{grid-column:span 4;}
    @media(max-width:950px){ .mosaic{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;} .span-1,.span-2,.span-3,.span-4{grid-column:span 1;} }
    ul { margin:0; padding-left:18px; }
    .pills { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
    .pills span { padding:5px 10px; border-radius:999px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); font-size:.82rem; color:#d8ddff; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <article class="glass">
        <span class="badge">Creative Tech Vibe</span>
        <h1>Elliot Mitchell crafts bold mobile experiences with rock-solid engineering foundations.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">This concept combines a modern “glass + gradient” visual language with clear sections for skills, work history, and project proof points—designed for memorable first impressions.</p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a href="mailto:elliot@elliotrmitchell.com">Contact</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/elliotrmitchell/">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/emitchel">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <aside class="glass">
        <h2>Fast Facts</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Android specialist with deep Kotlin and Java expertise.</li>
          <li>Built and improved production apps in safety, creator, and marketplace domains.</li>
          <li>Passion for observability, release confidence, and developer community engagement.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="mosaic">
      <article class="tile span-3">
        <h2>Work History Highlights</h2>
        <p>Hands-on contributor and technical leader with experience across mobile architecture, backend integration, and team mentorship. Frequent focus areas include app stability, performance optimization, and delivery predictability.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="tile span-3">
        <h2>Core Skills</h2>
        <div class="pills">
          <span>Kotlin</span><span>Java</span><span>Android</span><span>Firebase</span><span>Sentry</span><span>New Relic</span><span>Rails</span><span>JavaScript</span>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="tile span-2">
        <h2>Project: LiveSafe</h2>
        <p><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.livesafe.activities&hl=en_US&gl=US">View app</a></p>
      </article>
      <article class="tile span-2">
        <h2>Project: Outdoorsy</h2>
        <p><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.outdoorsy.owner&hl=en_US&gl=US">View app</a></p>
      </article>
      <article class="tile span-2">
        <h2>Project: Lens Distortions</h2>
        <p><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lensdistortions.ld&hl=en_US">View app</a></p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
